content:
Earn Skills as a Workforce Engagement Agent

Earn skills by taking enablement site (myTrailhead) modules that are assigned to you by your team lead. Leverage these skills for career growth opportunities later on.

Workforce Engagement is available in Lightning Experience and requires Enterprise, Performance, or Unlimited Editions.

To earn skills from agent engagement learning modules:

*   Workforce Engagement Analyst
*   Workforce Engagement Planner
*   Workforce Engagement Agent

Follow these steps:

1.  Open the Omni-Channel Widget.
2.  Click New to open a learning module assigned by your team lead.
3.  Complete each unit in the learning module.
4.  Go to Service Resources from the App Launcher and click on your profile.
5.  Scroll down to Related > Skills to view all earned skills.

See Workforce Engagement Retirement.
title: Workforce Engagement Agent Training
